name: DietBot
0: ”Alexa, tell diet bot to log meal”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: diet bot
des: You can say "tell diet bot to log meal" and subsequently say "I had..." or "I ate..." (some food) to log your meal. It will respond with the calories taken for the food and help you track your meal!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
